environment: strict repository-local trackers
repro_steps: Run pm plan create with Plan-specific fields while strict Plan policy requires generic metadata; retry the emitted --status or related suggestion and observe unknown-option failure.
resolution: "Plan creation now forwards shared governed create metadata through CLI, SDK, MCP, and contract surfaces."
expected_result: The plan workflow can satisfy the active Plan type policy or emits an executable recovery path.
actual_result: Strict creation reports missing generic fields that pm plan create cannot accept.
